name: Backstage Access (Ps. A Random Thoughts Collection)
description: This artpiece and the whole event itself I found myself. My art style that I consistently loving it piece by piece. We all know sometimes we are lost in our path, losing control on what is going on but we need to have a goal to know our deepest personality, to know who we really are. Knowing yourself is just like a infinity maze because we are growing day by day.
